.com/music/the-1975/chart-history/canadian-albums |title=The 1975 Chart History: Canadian Albums|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=9 June 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[GfK Entertainment Charts|GER]]<br><ref name=\"ger\">{{cite web|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/suche?artist_search=The+1975&do_search=do|title=Discographie The 1975|publisher=GfK Entertainment|accessdate=7 December 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Irish Albums Chart|IRE]]<br/><ref name=\"IRE\">{{cite web|url=http://irish-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=The+1975|title=Discography The 1975|website=irish-charts.com}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br/><ref name=\"NZL\">{{cite web|url=https://charts.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=The+1975 |title=Discography The 1975 |publisher=charts.nz. Hung Medien |accessdate=10 December 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Scottish Singles and Albums Charts|SCO]]<br><ref name=\"SCO albums\">{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/scottish-albums-chart/20130914/40/|title=2013-09-14 Top 40 Scottish Albums Archive|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=8 September 2013}}\n* ''A Brief Inquiry into Online Relationships'': {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/scottish-albums-chart/20181207/40/|title=2018-12-07 Scottish Albums Archive|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=8 December 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br/><ref name=\"swi\">{{cite web|url=http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=The+1975|title=The 1975 \u2013 Swiss Charts|publisher=Swisscharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=16 September 2013}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br/><ref name=\"US Billboard200\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/