es      = 21\n| Music videos = 24\n}}\n\nBritish [[alternative rock]] band [[The 1975]] has released three [[studio album]]s, a live album, five extended plays and twelve singles.\nThe band's debut album, ''[[The 1975 (album)|The 1975]]'' (2013), debuted at number one on the [[UK Albums Chart]] and was certified Platinum by the [[British Phonographic Industry]]. Its follow-up, ''[[I Like It When You Sleep, for You Are So Beautiful yet So Unaware of It]]'', was released on 26 February 2016.<ref name=\"NME October 2015\">{{Cite web|title=The 1975 say they are 'sick to death' of the lack of good pop music |url=http://www.nme.com/news/the-1975/88901 |website=[[NME]] |accessdate=9 October 2015 |date=8 October 2015}}</ref>\n\n==Albums==\n\n===Studio albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of albums, with selected chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:11em;\"| Sales\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:11em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\">UK chart positions:\n* All except noted: {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/27401/1975 |title=The 1975 |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=27 February 2015}}\n* \"Robbers\": {{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/140524cluk.txt |title=Chart: CLUK Update 24.05.2014 (wk20) |publisher=Zobbel.de |accessdate=25 June 2014 |author=Zywietz, Tobias}}\n* \"A Change of Heart\": {{cite web|title=CHART: CLUK Update 19.03.2016 (wk11)|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/160319cluk.txt|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=15 April 2016}}\n* \"She's American\": {{cite web|title=CHART: CLUK Update 5.03.2016 (wk9)|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/160305cluk.txt|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref name=\"AUS\">Australian chart positions:\n* All except noted: {{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=The+1975 |title=Discography The 1975 |website=Australian-charts.com |accessdate=3 November 2014}}\n* \"UGH!\": {{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/forum.asp?todo=viewthread&id=45576&pages=|title=ARIA Chartifacts 21-December-2015|publisher=Hung Medien|author=Ryan, Gavin (bulion)|accessdate=23 January 2016}}\n* \"The Sound\": {{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-singles-jonas-blue-fast-car-is-australias-no-1-song-20160130|title=ARIA Singles: Jonas Blue 'Fast Car' Is Australia's No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=30 January 2016|accessdate=30 January 2016}}\n* \"Give Yourself a Try\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2018/6/aria-chart-watch-476/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #476|publisher=auspOp|date=9 June 2018|accessdate=9 June 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br/><ref name=\"AUT\">{{cite web|url=http://austriancharts.at/showinterpret.asp?interpret=The+1975 |title=Discographie The 1975 |publisher=Austriancharts.at. Hung Medien |accessdate=3 November 2014}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]<br><ref name=\"CAN\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/the-1975/chart-history/canadian-albums |title=The 1975 Chart History: Canadian Albums|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=9 June 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[GfK Entertainment Charts|GER]]<br><ref name=\"ger\">{{cite web|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/suche?artist_search=The+1975&do_search=do|title=Discographie The 1975|publisher=GfK Entertainment|accessdate=7 December 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"co