he City |publisher=YouTube |date=25 April 2013 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UuihJInaeN4 |title=The 1975 - The City |via=YouTube |date=28 August 2013 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| Tim Mattia\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Sex\" {{small|(album version)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UKIhXi-yiw8 |title=The 1975 - Sex (Album Version) |via=YouTube |date=26 July 2013 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| [[Adam Powell (director)|Adam Powell]]<ref name=\"IMVDB\">{{cite web|url=https://imvdb.com/n/the-1975 |title=The 1975 |publisher=IMVDb |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Sex\" {{small|(acoustic version)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u7BhM8Qch44 |title=The 1975 - Sex |via=YouTube |date=12 August 2013 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| N/A\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Girls (The 1975 song)|Girls]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkubQCI4Fxo |title=The 1975 - Girls |via=YouTube |date=23 October 2013 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| Adam Powell<ref name=\"IMVDB\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Settle Down (The 1975 song)|Settle Down]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BsYE078RQCI |title=The 1975 - Settle Down |via=YouTube |date=21 January 2014 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2014\n| Nadia Otaen<ref name=\"IMVDB\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Robbers (song)|Robbers]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iyy3YOpxL2k |title=The 1975 - Robbers (Explicit) |via=YouTube |date=27 April 2014 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| Tim Mattia\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Heart Out\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9xA1Lvd37E |title=The 1975 - Heart Out |via=YouTube |date=7 September 2014 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| Matthew Healy, Adam Powell\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Love Me\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TJ5bZuUlftI |title=The 1975 - Love Me |via=YouTube |date=28 October 2015 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2015\n| [[Diane Martel]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"UGH!\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hXaU0QzByIM |title=The 1975 - UGH! |via=YouTube |date=18 December 2015 |accessdate=23 January 2016}}\n</ref>\n| Adam Powell\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"The Sound\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FSnAllHtG70 |title=The 1975 - The Sound |via=YouTube |date=25 February 2016 |accessdate=26 February 2016}}\n</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2016\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Tim Mattia\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"A Change of Heart\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=trbwqF0d7NA |title=The 1975 - A Change of Heart |via=YouTube |date=21 April 2016 |accessdate=28 April 2016}}\n</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Somebody Else\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/GBK3W1600484|title=The 1975 - Somebody Else |via=Vevo |date=7 July 2016 |accessdate=10 July 2016}}\n</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Give Yourself a Try\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vevo.com/watch/the-1975/give-yourself-a-try/GBUV71800848|title=The 1975 - Give Yourself A Try |via=Vevo |date=1 June 2018 |accessdate=1 June 2018}}\n</ref>\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2018\n| Diane Martel\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Love It If We Made It\" <small>(vertical video version)</small><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spin.com/2018/08/the-1975-love-it-if-we-made-it-vertical-video-watch/|title=Video: The 1975 \u2013 \u201cLove It If We Made It\u201d|accessdate=23 October 2018}}</ref>\n| Adam Powell\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"TooTimeTooTimeTooTime\"\n| N/A\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Love It If We Made It\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=1Wl1B7DPegc|title=The 1975 - Love It If We Made It|accessdate=21 October 2018}}</ref>\n| Adam Powell\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Sincerity Is Scary\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Warren Fu]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"It's Not Living (If It's Not With You)\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"People\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2019\n| Ben Ditto, Matthew Healy & Warren Fu\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Frail State of Mind\"\n| Matthew Healy, Patricia Villirillo & Mara Palena\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Me & You Together Song\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2020\n| bedroom\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"The Birthday Party\"\n| Ben Ditto & Jon Emmony\n|}\n\n==Songwriting and production credits==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Artist(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Album\n! scope=\"col\" | Contributing Member(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Credits\n! scope=\"col\" | Produced with:\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Pools to Bathe In\"\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 2015\n| rowspan=\"16\"| [[The Japanese House]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''[[Pools to Bathe In]]'' ''EP''\n| rowspan=\"8\"| Matthew Healy, George Daniel\n| rowspan=\"22\"| Producer\n| rowspan=\"16\"| The Japanese House\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Teeth\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Still\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Sister\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Clean\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[Clean (The Japanese House EP)|''Clean'']] ''EP''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Cool Blue\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Letter By The Water\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Sugar Pill\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Face Like Thunder\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2016\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''[[Swim Against the Tide]]'' ''EP''\n| rowspan=\"5\"| George Daniel\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Swim Against the Tide\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Good Side In\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Leon\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Saw You in a Dream (song)|Saw You in a Dream]]\"\n| rowspan=\"7\"| 2017\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''[[Saw You in a Dream]]'' ''EP''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Somebody You Found\"\n| Matthew Healy, George Daniel\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"3/3\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| George Daniel\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Count to Nine\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"White Whale\"\n| Colouring\n| ''Heathen EP''\n| Mikko Gordon, Luca Buccellati, Jack Kenworthy\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"There's a 